t/career\" class=\"chgrec-icon_link -white -hdr_nav_sub_btn\"><span class=\"chgrec-icon_link__icon\"><span class=\"chgrec-circle_icon -white\"><img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/assets-recruit/images/common/icon-line-arrow-right.svg\" alt=\"矢印アイコン\" class=\"js-svg\"></span></span><span class=\"c-heading6 chgrec-icon_link__text u-bold\">中途採用</span></a>\n                  </li>\n                  \n                </ul>\n              </div>\n              \n            </div>\n          </nav>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </header></div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"page-contents\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_page-contents-module-1\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n\n\n\n<div class=\"p-page_head -has_subtitle u-block\" style=\"background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(77, 114, 188,1.0) 0%, rgba(7, 7, 12,1.0) 100%);\">\n\n\t<div class=\"l-inner-default-pc l-inner-default-sp\">\n\t\t<h1 class=\"p-page_head__ttl -white\">プロジェクトストーリー</h1>\n\t\t\n\t</div>\n</div></div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_module_1698327624531\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n\n<section class=\"p-section -default\">\n  \n  \n  <div class=\"p-section__body\">\n    \n    <div class=\"l-inner-wide-pc l-inner-default-sp\">\n    \n      <div class=\"c-custom_html\">\n        <div class=\"addcg-project_story\">\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story01\"><img src=\"/hubfs/44116915/assets-recruit/images/project/img_project_t03.jpg\" alt=\"Project Story\">\n<p>「大手IT企業向け新入社員研修」の受注～開発。チーム全体で成し遂げた、大型プロジェクト</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">大型プロジェクト</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">DX教育</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story02\"> <img src=\"/hubfs/assets-recruit/images/project/img_pjs02_sumb.jpg\" alt=\"Project Story\">\n<p>DXで地方創生 村をまるごとデジタル化。<br>目の前の困りごとを解決し、未来を創る</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">DX支援・ITサービス</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">事業を創る</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">地方創生</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story03\"> <img src=\"/hubfs/assets-recruit/images/project/img_project_t03_main.jpg\" alt=\"Project Story\">\n<p>人材育成プラットフォーム『KaWaL』立ち上げ。<br>新規事業と新人メンバー成長の軌跡</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新規事業開発</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新たな学習スタイル</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story04\"> <img src=\"/hubfs/assets-recruit/images/project/img_pjs04_sumb.jpg\" alt=\"Project Story\">\n<p>東京メトロを変えたDXプロジェクト。<br>新デバイスでつくる検査業務の「新」常識</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">DX支援・ITサービス</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">ビジネスプロセスを創る</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">現場改革</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story05\"> <img src=\"/hubfs/assets-recruit/images/project/img_pjs05_sumb.jpg\" alt=\"Project Story\">\n<p>OJTをサポートするSaaSの開発。<br>『OJT One』を育てることと、成長すること</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新規事業開発</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">組織変革</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story06\"><img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/pj06%E3%82%B5%E3%83%A0%E3%83%8D%E3%82%A4%E3%83%AB.jpg\" alt=\"pj06サムネイル\">\n<p>新卒1年目から大舞台へ。<br>100社超コンソーシアムを支えた秘訣とは</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">DX支援・ITサービス</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">若手の活躍</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">大型プロジェクト</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story07\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/Mask%20group-2%20(1).png\">\n<p>日本を代表する大手企業グループの研修プログラム。<br>入社半年の若手社員がつかんだビッグチャンス</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">若手の活躍</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">リーダー育成</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story08\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/44116915/HP%E5%85%A8%E4%BD%93%E6%8E%B2%E8%BC%89%E5%86%99%E7%9C%9F.png\">\n<p>ANA大阪空港×チェンジ×ビーキャップ。<br>3社連携で実現した現場の業務改革</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">IT・DX支援</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新卒社員</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">中途社員</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">早期活躍</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.change-jp.com/projectstory09\"> <img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%E7%94%BB%E9%9D%A2%20(1).png\">\n<p>“日本を変える”ために飛び込んだ。<br>北海道から、地方創生の新モデルを創る</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">チェンジ北海道</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">AI</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">中途社員</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">新規事業立ち上げ</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/recruit/project/story10\"><img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%E7%94%BB%E9%9D%A2%20(1)-1.png\" alt=\"Project Story\">\n<p>生成AI研修をつくるという挑戦。正解のない世界で、私たちはどこまで成長できるのか。</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">人材育成</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">生成AI</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">DX教育</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/projectstory12\" rel=\"noopener\" linktext=\"答えのない現場で、考え続けた二人の挑戦 ──建築部の未来をゼロから描き直すまで\n\nIT・DX支援\n業務改善\n社会インフラ\"><img src=\"https://www.change-jp.com/hubfs/%E4%B8%80%E8%A6%A7%E7%94%BB%E9%9D%A2%20(3).png\" alt=\"Project Story\">\n<p>答えのない現場で、考え続けた二人の挑戦 ──建築部の未来をゼロから描き直すまで</p>\n<div class=\"addcg-label\">\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">IT・DX支援</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">業務改善</div>\n<div class=\"addcg-label01\">社会インフラ</div>\n</div>\n</a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  \n</section></div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div id=\"foot-contents\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0